WEBVTT

00:01.006 --> 00:05.126
I saw them at the guest cottage,
him and the Jew.

00:05.375 --> 00:07.733
They're rutting at Ash Park.

00:07.735 --> 00:10.813
If you even think
of marrying this woman,

00:10.815 --> 00:13.933
Ash Park will go to James.

00:13.935 --> 00:16.733
What sort of man do you think I am?

00:16.735 --> 00:21.013
I won't have our baby born
into her pit of poison.

00:21.015 --> 00:22.535
Livvy?

00:30.375 --> 00:34.375
We should go. To the city.
You were right.

00:34.468 --> 00:38.186
The child that I gave away
to be raised by others -

00:38.188 --> 00:39.946
it was you.

00:39.948 --> 00:45.106
I'll marry Gino,
and I will have the baby.

00:45.108 --> 00:46.908
Marry me.

00:48.601 --> 00:54.107
Subtitles by MemoryOnSmells
http://UKsubtitles.ru.

00:58.028 --> 01:00.108
You may have overplayed your hand.

01:01.308 --> 01:03.468
Then I'll deal another.

01:05.548 --> 01:08.668
Of course I want to say yes.
Then say it.

01:10.268 --> 01:11.906
Why now?

01:11.908 --> 01:14.546
I know what I want now.
Why the sudden urgency?

01:14.548 --> 01:16.946
Does it matter?
Yes.

01:16.948 --> 01:20.468
Mother threatened to disinherit me
if we stay together.

01:21.468 --> 01:23.506
So this is... defiance?

01:23.508 --> 01:24.586
No.

01:24.588 --> 01:26.906
I'm doing something
I should have done weeks ago.

01:26.908 --> 01:29.946
But we're happy with the way it is.
I'm not.

01:29.948 --> 01:32.226
You deserve to be
more than my mistress.

01:32.228 --> 01:36.866
You deserve more than stolen moments
and a charade in public.

01:36.868 --> 01:38.708
There are practicalities, George.
Damn them.

01:42.868 --> 01:46.468
What does your heart say? Say it.

01:48.948 --> 01:51.348
Yes.

01:53.000 --> 01:59.074
